    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Bloody Eyes Can&apos;t Tell",
        "Description": "Agent 47,\r\rI am hosting a small gathering, and you are to be the guest of honor. I take pride in my parties as much as my work, as much as world domination is all the better with canap\u00e9s.\r\rNaturally, your presence is not merely requested as it is expected. After all, a party is so dreadfully dull without it&apos;s most prominent gatecrasher.\r\rDon&apos;t forget to try our best wine. It is absolutely to die for.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Switcher.",
